# Portfolio Project

Personal portfolio — static site deployed to GitHub Pages.

## Stack

- **Language:** JavaScript (ES modules, `'use strict'`)
- **Build:** Vite 7 (`app/pages` as root)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 4 (`@import 'tailwindcss'`, `@theme`, `@utility`, `@layer`)
- **Carousel:** Splide
- **Lint:** ESLint (flat config) + Prettier
- **Deploy:** GitHub Actions → GitHub Pages (`/portfolio` base path)

## Path Aliases

| Alias | Resolves to |
|-------|-------------|
| `#`   | `src/`      |
| `@`   | `app/`      |

## Architecture (Atomic Design)

```
app/
  atoms/        — small self-contained UI (btn-top, cursor)
  molecules/    — composed behavior (nav, achievements, cases)
  pages/        — entry points (index.html, index.js)

src/
  styles/       — globals.css (Tailwind theme + components)
  utils/        — pure helpers (is-mobile, theme, etc.)
```

## Key Conventions

- No framework — vanilla DOM manipulation via `init*()` functions
- Each module exports a single `initModuleName()` called from `index.js`
- Event listeners always use `{ passive: true }` where possible
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` for animations/scroll behavior
- Russian language for user-facing content
- `public/` holds static assets (images, fonts, documents)
